title: Swedish Midlaner LF Competitive Team
body:
Recently moved to Darwin from Sweden, looking for a team to play with. I´m preferably looking for a consistent team with high ambitions.

On EUW I have been around Dia4-Dia1 the past 4 seasons, here on OCE I´m currently P3 but will be back to my old rank soon enough (been having slight internet issues here in the NT).

I have plenty of time to spare and would be able to practice daily, and even move if need be.

Hit me up in-game for any questions,

Sir Pumpernickel
